bio.employment: Director of Sales in the Transportation World & Turo Host - Vehicle & Transportation Expert!  :)
bio.openEndedText:
My wife Jhana and I started Turo in 2023 with the intent to help people be able to rent cars much more efficiently than at Car Rental companies.  We have traveled quite a bit over the last 5+ years and realized Car Rental Companies at times can be a pain in the you know what!  :(  Also, the customer experience is not always the best.  We wanted to change that experience.  Plus, we absolutely love cars and are car enthusiasts.  We appreciate you as our guests and hope that your experience is flawless with us.  My wife is a stay-at-home mom, grandma and dog mom.  I am a Director of Sales for a School Bus and Commercial & Transit Bus Dealership in Southern California.  We hope to Host you soon!  Take Care and drive safe!

PS: We currently have a 2012 Blue Fiat 500 Lounge, 2012 Black Toyota Camry, 2013 Red Fiat 500 Pop, 2013 Green Fiat 500 Pop, White 2014 Toyota Corolla, White 2017 Subaru Forester Touring AWD, White 2019 Range Rover Velar S-Dynamic, a Light Gray/Silver 2021 Dodge Challenger SXT, a White 2021 Chevy Silverado Crew Cab Long Bed, 2022 Blue Toyota Corolla SE and should have 3-5 additional vehicles on our platform by the end of summer 2024.  We are also looking to co-host your vehicle.  Reach out if interested.  

Ride On...........    :)

Sincerely,
Jason & Jhana
The Cargivers
